      "options": {
        "content": "## Langfuse Correlation\nUse the same `sessionId`, `turnId`, `traceId`, and `providerObservationId` to pivot between Grafana and Langfuse.\n\nOperational scores written on terminal turns:\n- `chat_turn_outcome`\n- `chat_turn_success`\n- `chat_turn_resume_success`\n- `chat_turn_duration_ms`\n- `chat_turn_ttft_ms`\n- `chat_turn_pause_effective_ms`\n- `chat_turn_prompt_fallback`\n- `chat_provider_stop_reason`\n- `chat_provider_output_tokens`\n\nThese scores are heuristic runtime evaluations, not semantic quality judgments.",
